automerge-windows is a pre-built binary overlay port.

CMake integration:

    find_package(automerge-windows CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(my_app PRIVATE automerge::wrapper)

Provided targets:
    automerge::wrapper  — C++ wrapper static lib + headers
    automerge::core     — Rust native DLL (automerge_core.dll)

Note: automerge_core.dll must be deployed alongside your executable.
      With the vcpkg + CMake toolchain integration this is handled automatically.

Installing (overlay port):
    vcpkg install automerge-windows --overlay-ports=<repo-root>/ports
